Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon Demon! Attack Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All right! All the Toons were destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! It was your courage\N that defeated the Toons!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Exactly what I would expect from\N﻿one chosen by the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It seems I was\N playing around {\i1}far{\i0} too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, from now on,\N this will be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a fight between two people chosen by the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's settle this in a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dark Game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Evil Eye is Activated:\N Sacrifice"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bakura... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm not the Bakura you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm an ancient soul resting deep within one of the Millennium Items, the Millennium Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Millennium Ring...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All I require is the key to the contracts for Kaiba ﻿Corporation that Mokuba has cleverly hidden away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you're a good boy and hand me Mokuba,\N﻿I'll turn everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, no matter what I say to Bakura, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he really being controlled by that Millennium Ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:03:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll hand this brat over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Forgive me, Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's this thing's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now, the Dark Game shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The whole arena... is being taken over by darkness...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dark Game...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Those two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I was able to rescue Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's wrong with Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's alright. He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿To be honest, I don't believe it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What happened? Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't tell anything from up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's go down and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry, but these guys'll just have to wait here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿From this point on, this is a wizard's battle\N﻿that no normal being can endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, I wonder how your other mind will hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My other self can't handle this Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Other I! I'll draw the cards from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if we don't fight together, Pegasus' Millennium ﻿Eye will be able to see through you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be alright! Let me fight with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Eyes Illusionist in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This guy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In a Dark Game, the Duel Rings Kaiba Corporation created are no longer active.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The players' willpower literally brings the Monsters to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that willpower should run out, the player's life might run out as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark Eyes Illusionist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An Illusion Monster\N with 0 Attack and Defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}I can't just charge in and attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to have some sort of Special Ability...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Curse of Dragon to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take over and let you think of a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mind Shuffle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you switched souls again, keeping me from reading your mind..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi boy lacks the mentality ﻿needed to fight in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My chest... hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The burden of maintaining the Monsters' real form is draining the other me's willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there, other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, the other Yugi is merely a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He'll soon run out of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's wrong, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't explain it, but... I feel like Yugi's in pain inside that black dark bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's not your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A second ago, my chest just hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You too, Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Not long ago, I saw Bakura bring the Monsters on his cards to ﻿life using what he called "the Power of Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm sure we've experienced this "Power of Darkness" before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I will set a card face-down on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a limit to my other self's mental strength...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let this battle\N drag on any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿On my turn, I'll attack with Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have fallen for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You rushed into battle to protect the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was my aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate\N Dark Eyes Illusionist's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Eyes Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In exchange for having no Attack or Defense Points, it is given a Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of its Evil Eye, Dark Eyes Illusionist can steal away its opponent's abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But the true terror of my Illusion Monsters has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Ritual! I will activate this card with Dark Eyes Illusionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I Summon the Illusion Monster, Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A Ritual Summon Monster?! Sacrifice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I activate Sacrifice's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Curse of Dragon is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician, attack Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice Shield!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's using the absorbed Curse of Dragon as a shield to block the attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician's attack has taken out Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I took damage to my Life instead...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice gains the Attack and Defense of any of the opponent's Monsters it absorbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, when the player attacks the shield of Sacrifice, they take damage to their own Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sacrifice...! ﻿What a terrible Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I use Sacrifice's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Dark Eyes Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control Black Magician\N with the Evil Eye's spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be absorbed by Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's using Black Magician as a shield...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice now gains the Attack and Defense points of your Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you attack him, your own Life will be\N﻿reduced. What will you do, Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my invincible Illusion Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?\N How do I defeat Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't think of anything to do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't take action, Pegasus will just read your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll buy you some time to think of a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your mental strength is already at its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't risk it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If your menial strength should reach its limit, your soul will eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your mind is fading away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please.... let me draw one final card...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A card that can defeat Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I... set a card face-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Gremlin in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use this card... to defeat... Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems this is the end of the line for other mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice, ﻿attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there, my other self!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You have to defeat Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Goodbye, other Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What...? I just felt something really bad just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Could it be something happened to Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang in there! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I beg you... snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It seems the other mind of Yugi boy just wasn't\N﻿up to the right level to play in a Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now your other mind has perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are we really not able to get into that field of darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can all we do is just stand here and do nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All we're good for is standing here staring...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿An...zu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright, I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey Honda, are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dammit! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I went through to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So we can't interfere with those playing a Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Our friend's in a really bad situation...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And we can't even go in and support him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe... if our hearts are able to somehow reach him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿However, Yugi boy... now that your\N﻿other mind has disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The only thing stopping my Millennium Eye,\N﻿your Mind Shuffle, has been sealed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Even so, do you still intend on continuing to Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Until my heart breaks in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿...there's no "game over"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Continue the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's your turn, Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Scan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card you have just drawn is Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Normal Monster Card with 1400 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every card in my hand has been read by Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only one Pegasus doesn't know is the set card my other self placed on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice but to bet everything on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress In Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In that case, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice Illusion: Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Winged Dragon, Guardian of the\N﻿Fortress has been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And the Time Bomber card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Bomb Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Bomber is a self destructing Monster that cannot be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In two turns, its Special Ability will destroy\N﻿every Monster on my side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In two turns, Sacrifice will be destroyed by Time Bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, your Monster as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sacrifice has 0 Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So if it's destroyed, Pegasus' Life Points won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if Black Magician is destroyed along with Sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}...those points... will be deducted from my Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿{\i1}If this Sacrifice Combo works, I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, can you stop this combo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk the path of destruction!\N That is the Sacrifice Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two turns left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no cards in my hand that can stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if there were, Pegasus read them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have to draw a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Pegasus' Millennium Eye will see it at the same time I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the Mind Scan,\N you can't do a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose! It's game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Within the Dark Game, Yugi fights alone in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We won't take just not being able to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Our hearts are strongly connected through friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, connect your heart with ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We'll lend you the strength to defeat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fusion of Light and Darkness:\N Black Chaos Descends"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
